# GYM LMS CRM (Next.js + TypeScript)

A frontend web application for managing gym-related workflows, built with **Next.js** and **TypeScript**.  
This project focuses on building a clean, responsive, and scalable user interface for a gym LMS/CRM system.

---

## ğŸ“Œ Overview

This project was developed during an industry internship to gain hands-on experience with **Next.js** and **TypeScript** in a real-world environment.  
It demonstrates component-based architecture, reusable UI patterns, and dashboard-style layouts commonly used in management systems.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- Responsive UI built with Next.js and TypeScript
- Reusable and well-structured components
- Dashboard-style layouts for gym management
- Forms and pages for managing gym-related data
- Focus on clean UI, maintainability, and performance

